lic_en", "text": "faults,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "by reason of my confidence in him: (A 'Obeyd, O, TA:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I acquainted him with my whole state,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "case; not concealing from him anything thereof."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(As, TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^uHad~ivuhu biEujariY wabujariY", "text_ar": "اُحَدِّثُهُ بِعُجَرِى وَبُجَرِى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I relate to"}, {"kind": "page_break", "n": 1959}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "him my vices,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "faults."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ya$okuw Eujarahu", "text_ar": "يَشْكُو عُجَرَهُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "wabujarahu", "text_ar": "وَبُجَرَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He complains of his vices,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "faults,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the like:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of his sorrows:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of what is apparent and what is concealed."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, * TA. [In the CK,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aubodira", "text_ar": "اُبْدِرَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is put by mistake for"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ubodiYa", "text_ar": "اُبْدِىَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".]) One says also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jaA='a fulaAnN biAlEujari waAlbujari", "text_ar": "جَا=ءَ فُلَانٌ بِالعُجَرِ وَالبُجَرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  i. e. ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one uttered"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "falsehood:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a great,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "terrible, thing."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Fr, TA.) [See, again,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bujorapN", "text_ar": "بُجْرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".] ―         -b5-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EujorapN", "text_ar": "عُجْرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "also signifies The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "mark made upon the waist by the running string of the drawers."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, TA.) To this a poet likens the mark made by a blunt sword. (Aboo-Sa'eed, TA.) ―         -b6-  And one says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Als~ayofN fiY firinodihi EujarN", "text_ar": "السَّيْفٌ فِى فِرِنْدِهِ عُجَرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The sword has, in its diversified wavy marks, what resemble knots"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "Mgh", "O", "K", "As", "TA", "IAth"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}